data.name: label1.Text
data.value: Essential Diagram ships with a Symbol Designer Utility, which facilitates the creation of custom symbols. These symbols can be organized in various categoies for ease of use. Furthermore, symbols can also imported in the form of Microsoft Visio stencils files(*.vss files), which can be converted into Essential Diagram symbol palettes. These symbol palette can also be edited and customized according to the needs of the user.
